  <entry>
    <title type="html"><![CDATA[Escaping Characters in Octopress]]></title>
    <link href="http://ccphan.github.io/blog/2014/09/04/escaping-characters-in-octopress/"/>
    <updated>2014-09-04T19:38:44+09:00</updated>
    <id>http://ccphan.github.io/blog/2014/09/04/escaping-characters-in-octopress</id>
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>To ensure that a particular content block won&rsquo;t be parsed by Liquid and displayed &lsquo;as is&rsquo; you can enclose the block contents in <code>&lt;% raw %&gt;</code> and <code>&lt;% endraw %&gt;</code> tag.</p>

<p>Example - displaying an xml snippet (replace <code>[</code> with <code>{</code> in example):</p>

<figure class='code'><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
<span class='line-number'>2</span>
<span class='line-number'>3</span>
<span class='line-number'>4</span>
<span class='line-number'>5</span>
<span class='line-number'>6</span>
<span class='line-number'>7</span>
<span class='line-number'>8</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class='xml'><span class='line'>[% codeblock lang:xml file.xml %]
</span><span class='line'>  [% raw %]
</span><span class='line'>    <span class="nt">&lt;entry&gt;</span>
</span><span class='line'>    ...
</span><span class='line'>    <span class="nt">&lt;content</span> <span class="na">type=</span><span class="s">&quot;html&quot;</span><span class="nt">&gt;</span><span class="cp">&lt;![CDATA[{{ post.content | expand_urls: site.url | markdownize | cdata_escape }}]]&gt;</span><span class="nt">&lt;/content&gt;</span>
</span><span class='line'>    <span class="nt">&lt;/entry&gt;</span>
</span><span class='line'>  [% endraw %]
</span><span class='line'>[% endcodeblock %]
</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>


<!-- more -->


<p>It&rsquo;ll appear like:</p>

<figure class='code'><figcaption><span>file.xml </span></figcaption>
<div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
<span class='line-number'>2</span>
<span class='line-number'>3</span>
<span class='line-number'>4</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class='xml'><span class='line'><span class="nt">&lt;entry&gt;</span>
</span><span class='line'>...
</span><span class='line'><span class="nt">&lt;content</span> <span class="na">type=</span><span class="s">&quot;html&quot;</span><span class="nt">&gt;</span><span class="cp">&lt;![CDATA[{{ post.content | expand_urls: site.url | markdownize | cdata_escape }}]]&gt;</span><span class="nt">&lt;/content&gt;</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="nt">&lt;/entry&gt;</span>
</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>

]]></content>
